## Environment Variables Reference

| Variable | Required | Description |
|----------|----------|-------------|
| `APP_ENV` | yes | `dev`, `test`, or `prod` |
| `APP_SECRET` | yes | Random 32+ character secret |
| `DATABASE_URL` | yes | Full DSN for the database |
{% if use_auth and auth_method == "jwt" %}
| `JWT_SECRET_KEY` | yes | Path to the JWT private key |
| `JWT_PUBLIC_KEY` | yes | Path to the JWT public key |
| `JWT_PASSPHRASE` | yes | Passphrase for the JWT key pair |
| `JWT_TTL` | no | Token TTL in seconds (default: 3600) |
{% elif use_auth and auth_method == "oauth2" %}
| `OAUTH2_CLIENT_ID` | yes | OAuth2 client identifier |
| `OAUTH2_CLIENT_SECRET` | yes | OAuth2 client secret |
| `OAUTH2_REDIRECT_URI` | yes | OAuth2 redirect URI |
{% elif use_auth and auth_method == "api-key" %}
| `API_KEY_HEADER` | no | Header name (default: X-API-Key) |
{% endif %}
{% if use_rabbitmq %}
| `MESSENGER_TRANSPORT_DSN` | yes | AMQP DSN for RabbitMQ |
{% endif %}
{% if use_redis %}
| `REDIS_URL` | yes | Redis DSN |
{% endif %}
| `MAILER_DSN` | no | SMTP DSN for email sending |

## Useful Console Commands

```bash
# Clear cache
php bin/console cache:clear

# List all routes
php bin/console debug:router

# List all services
php bin/console debug:container

# Generate a new entity
php bin/console make:entity

# Create a migration after entity changes
php bin/console make:migration

# Apply pending migrations
php bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate

# Check migration status
php bin/console doctrine:migrations:status
{% if use_auth %}

# Create a user (if UserFixtures exist)
php bin/console app:user:create --email=user@example.com --role=ROLE_USER
{% endif %}
{% if use_rabbitmq %}

# Consume messages from the queue
php bin/console messenger:consume async --limit=10
{% endif %}
```

## Deployment

See [Architecture](docs/architecture.md) and [Ways of Working](docs/ways-of-working.md) for full deployment guidance.

Quick checklist:

- [ ] Set `APP_ENV=prod` and `APP_DEBUG=0`
- [ ] Run `composer install --no-dev --optimize-autoloader`
- [ ] Run `php bin/console cache:warmup`
- [ ] Run `php bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate --no-interaction`
- [ ] Ensure `var/` and `public/` are writable by the web server user
- [ ] Configure a process manager (Supervisor) for Messenger workers if async messaging is used

